name: Antarctic Krill Oil 500mg Omega 3 Fatty Acid Supplement, MegaRed Extra Strength EPA & DHA Softgels (90cnt box), Antioxidant Astaxanthin, Heart Health Supplement With No Fish Oil Aftertaste
feature_bullets: ANTARCTIC KRILL OIL: Krill is one of the world’s most abundant and sustainable organisms. MegaRed only sources krill from the Antarctic where krill is most abundant.,OMEGA 3 SUPPLEMENT: MegaRed Omega 3 Krill Oil has been shown to significantly increase your omega 3 index in just 30 days. Supportive research has shown that consumption of EPA and DHA omega-3 fatty acids may reduce the risk of coronary heart disease.,HEART HEALTH: MegaRed Omega 3 Krill Oil supplements provide an optimal combination of omega-3 fatty acids and the powerful antioxidant astaxanthin to support heart health in a once daily softgel.,3X MORE PURE: MegaRed with PureTechTM is 3x MORE PURE than regular krill oil. Salts and other impurities are removed to provide the purest krill oil on the market.,NO FISHY AFTERTASTE and EASY ABSORPTION: Krill Oil is carried in a phospholipid form which is better absorbed by the human body and because it's krill oil as opposed to fish oil, MegaRed Krill Oil has no fishy aftertaste or odor.,These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease.

name: Carlson - Super D Omega-3, Wild-Caught Norwegian Arctic Cod Liver Oil, 2000 IU (50 mcg) Vitamin D3, 1100 mg Omega-3s, Sustainably Sourced Nordic Fish Oil Liquid, Lemon, 250 ml
feature_bullets: HEART, BRAIN, AND IMMUNE HEALTH - A single teaspoonful of Carlson Super D Omega-3 provides 1,100 mg of omega-3s, including EPA and DHA, which support heart, brain, vision, and joint health, plus 2,000 IU (50 mcg) of vitamin D3 which promotes immune health. To ensure maximum freshness, Super D Omega-3 is closely managed from sea to store.,AWARD-WINNING TASTE AND QUALITY - Super D Omega-3 in delicious natural lemon flavor has received numerous awards for it's taste and quality. The world-renowned chefs and sommeliers at the International Taste and Quality Institute honored Super D Omega-3 with a Superior Taste Award.,SUSTAINABLY SOURCED - We source the highest quality Arctic cod off the coast of Norway using traditional, sustainable methods. The same day they're caught, our Nordic cod are transported to a highly regulated Norwegian facility for processing and purification.,IFOS AND IGEN NON-GMO CERTIFIED - Carlson omega-3s are approved by the International Fish Oil Standards (IFOS) program, the only third-party testing and certification program exclusively for fish oil supplements, and are certified non-GMO by the International Genetically Modified Organism Evaluation and Notification (IGEN) program.,FRESHNESS, POTENCY, AND PURITY GUARANTEED - Carlson Super D Omega-3 is bottled with a touch of antioxidants and is given a nitrogen flush to remove oxygen and to prevent oxidation. Like all Carlson omega-3s, freshness, potency, and purity are guaranteed.,During the summer months products may arrive warm but Amazon stores and ships products in accordance with manufacturers' recommendations, when provided.
